; Coverage for xact.cc (memoized_results in auto_xact)
; When the same account appears in multiple transactions, the
; memoized results are reused for faster evaluation.

= Expenses:Food
    (Budget:Food)    -1

2024/01/01 Grocery1
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Grocery2
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Grocery3
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget
24-Jan-01 Grocery1              (Budget:Food)               $-10.00      $-10.00
24-Jan-02 Grocery2              (Budget:Food)               $-20.00      $-30.00
24-Jan-03 Grocery3              (Budget:Food)               $-30.00      $-60.00
end test
